  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下数据平台的整体架构。核心是一个数据管理器（Gestor de Dados），它负责协调多个数据源和前端展示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GestorDados"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Gestor de Dados 是中心节点。它上游有什么触发机制吗？还是被动接收请求？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GestorDados"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有个调度器 Scheduler 会定期触发它，用\"Estimula\"这个关系。Scheduler 是数据库形态的节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCHD",
        "GestorDados"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我添加了 Scheduler 指向 Gestor de Dados 的箭头，标注\"Estimula\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCHD",
        "GestorDados"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Gestor de Dados 处理完数据后，有两条输出路径：一条是保存到缓存管理器 Gestor Cache，另一条是发送消息到 RabbitMQ。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GestorDados",
